<body>
<p class="p1">&lt;!-- Tools panel injected by BuildAllFromMaster.sh --&gt;</p>
<p class="p1">&lt;section class="tools" style="margin:16px 0 20px;"&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>&lt;style&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>.tools .row{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px}</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>.tools .tbtn{</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">      </span>display:inline-block;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:10px;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">      </span>background:#0e49c2;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;white-space:nowrap</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>}</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>.tools p{margin:.35rem 0 0;color:#475467;font-size:.95rem}</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>&lt;/style&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>&lt;h2 style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:18px;"&gt;Tools&lt;/h2&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>&lt;div class="row"&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;!-- Open Bridge (Master) --&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;a class="tbtn"</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">       </span>href="file:///Volumes/Extreme%20SSD/Backup_Files_To_NAS/Bridge_Photo_Shortcuts/Open_Bridge_Using_Master.command"&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">       </span>Open Bridge (Master)</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;/a&gt;</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;!-- Build &amp; Open Workflow Hub --&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;a class="tbtn"</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">       </span>href="file:///Volumes/Extreme%20SSD/Backup_Files_To_NAS/Bridge_Photo_Shortcuts/Build_And_Open_Hub.command"&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">       </span>Build &amp;amp; Open Workflow Hub</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;/a&gt;</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;!-- Send Photos to SanDisk --&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;a class="tbtn"</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">       </span>href="file:///Volumes/Extreme%20SSD/Backup_Files_To_NAS/Bridge_Photo_Shortcuts/Send_Photos_To_SanDisk.command"&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">       </span>Send Photos to SanDisk</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;/a&gt;</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;!-- Open Bridge (Shot Dates: Pick Year) --&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;a class="tbtn"</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">       </span>href="file:///Volumes/Extreme%20SSD/Backup_Files_To_NAS/Bridge_Photo_Shortcuts/Open_Bridge_Shot_Dates_Pick_Year.command"&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">       </span>Open Bridge (Shot Dates: Pick Year)</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;/a&gt;</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;!-- Edit MASTER-steps.txt (direct open of the text file) --&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;a class="tbtn"</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">       </span>href="file:///Volumes/Extreme%20SSD/Backup_Files_To_NAS/PhotographyHub/pages/MASTER-steps.txt"&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">       </span>Edit MASTER-steps.txt</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>&lt;/a&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>&lt;/div&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>&lt;p&gt;Tip: For best results opening &lt;code&gt;.command&lt;/code&gt; buttons, use Safari.&lt;/p&gt;</p>
<p class="p1">&lt;/section&gt;</p>
</body>
</html>
